CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1773288217
OL,3,CHome Secretary grants police request
OL,4,Cto ban Al Quds Day march
OL,6,F"I expect to see the full force of the
OL,7,Flaw applied to anyone spreading hatred
OL,8,Fand division instead of exercising
OL,9,Ftheir right to peaceful protest."
OL,11,FThe Islamic Human Rights Commission
OL,12,F(IHRC), which organises the protest,
OL,13,Fhas previously insisted the march is
OL,14,Falways "good-natured and peaceful"
OL,16,FThe IHRC confirmed that a "static
OL,17,Fprotest" will go ahead on Sunday, in a
OL,18,Fstatement published on their website.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
