PN,31804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1773288217
OL,3,CHome Secretary grants police request
OL,4,Cto ban Al Quds Day march
OL,6,F"The police have brazenly abandoned
OL,7,Ftheir sworn principle of policing
OL,8,Fwithout fear or favour. They cannot
OL,9,Fpresent evidence because there is none.
OL,11,F"In essence, this is a politically
OL,12,Fcharged decision, not one taken for
OL,13,Fthe security of the people of London."
OL,15,FThe IHRC said it "strongly condemns"
OL,16,Fthe decision and was seeking legal
OL,17,Fadvice.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUuD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
