PN,31806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1773288217
OL,3,CHome Secretary grants police request
OL,4,Cto ban Al Quds Day march
OL,6,FThe Met said the "uniquely complex"
OL,7,Finternational situation and "severe"
OL,8,Frisks meant merely placing conditions
OL,9,Fon the protest "will not be sufficient
OL,10,Fto prevent it from resulting in
OL,11,Fserious public disorder".
OL,13,FIt added that it would place "strict
OL,14,Fconditions" on any static protest,
OL,15,Fwhich the law does not allow the
OL,16,Fpolice or government to ban, but
OL,17,F"given the tensions, we have to accept
OL,18,Fthat confrontations could still take
OL,19,Fplace".
