OL,3,CHome Secretary grants police request
OL,4,Cto ban Al Quds Day march
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FLabour and Conservative MPs had called
OL,12,Ffor the march to be banned.
OL,14,FEarlier on Tuesday, courts minister
OL,15,FSarah Sackman said people expressing
OL,16,Fsupport for "the malign regime in
OL,17,FIran" should not be "on the streets of
OL,18,FLondon calling for hate and hostility
OL,19,Fagainst this country".
OL,26,@xD@MOUyD@EO]yD@UOU{D@UO]
