OL,3,CHome Secretary grants police request
OL,4,Cto ban Al Quds Day march
OL,6,FShadow Home Office minister Alicia
OL,7,FKearns also called for the march to be
OL,8,Fcancelled, saying there was "no place
OL,9,Fin our country for the celebration of
OL,10,Fterrorists".
OL,12,FA spokesman for the IHRC, Faisal Bodi,
OL,13,Ftold the BBC's The World Tonight that
OL,14,Fit was "a sad day for freedom of
OL,15,Fexpression, freedom of assembly and
OL,16,Fthe right of people to legitimately
OL,17,Fprotest about issues they feel
OL,18,Fstrongly about".
