OL,3,CHome Secretary grants police request
OL,4,Cto ban Al Quds Day march
OL,6,FHe added, "This demonstration has
OL,7,Ftaken place for the last 40 years
OL,8,Fpeacefully."
OL,10,FThe IHRC has previously expressed
OL,11,Fsupport for Iran's former supreme
OL,12,Fleader, the Ayatollah Ali Khamenei.
OL,14,FFollowing his death in a US-Israeli
OL,15,Fairstrike last month, the group said
OL,16,FKhamenei "chose to stand on the right
OL,17,Fside of history" and described him as
OL,18,F"a rare role model" who would be
OL,19,F"mourned by freedom-loving people all
OL,20,Fover the world".
