OL,3,CHome Secretary grants police request
OL,4,Cto ban Al Quds Day march
OL,6,FThe Campaign Against Antisemitism
OL,7,Fwelcomed the decision to ban the
OL,8,Fmarch, saying it was "a positive
OL,9,Fdevelopment" and adding: "Allowing
OL,10,Fthis hate-fest to go ahead would have
OL,11,Fsent the message that Islamists rule
OL,12,Fthe roost in Britain."
